[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1589},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fpython\u002F20210926\u002F4028850576\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fpython\u002F20210926\u002F4028850576\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fpython\u002F20210926\u002F4028850576\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fpython\u002F20210926\u002F4028850576\u002F":1566,"related:\u002Fpython\u002F20210926\u002F4028850576\u002F":1575},"\u002Fen\u002Fpython\u002F2021\u002F09\u002F26\u002Fpython-25-exception-handling\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1549,"date":1550,"description":18,"extension":1551,"lang":1552,"meta":1553,"navigation":57,"path":1554,"readingMinutes":1555,"seo":1556,"standalone":1557,"stem":1558,"tags":1559,"tldr":1563,"updated":1563,"url":1564,"__hash__":1565},"content\u002F從 JavaScript 角度學 Python\u002F從-JavaScript-角度學-Python-25-例外處理.md","從 JavaScript 角度學 Python(25) - 例外處理","4028850576",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1538},"minimark",[11,15,19,22,25,41,153,163,170,173,176,179,214,221,227,235,238,284,290,293,306,359,370,373,384,478,481,487,491,498,690,713,877,883,892,1051,1061,1067,1126,1132,1138,1141,1162,1168,1370,1390,1399,1402,1456,1465,1468,1471,1474,1477,1493,1496,1528,1534],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來我們要聊一個非常非常重要的東西，也就是關於錯誤的處理，而這個處理又稱之為例外處理。",[12,20,21],{"id":21},"例外處理概念",[16,23,24],{},"首先先聊聊例外處理是什麼，通常我們在開發系統的時候不免會遇到一些錯誤狀況，例如：使用者網路不穩定、使用者輸入錯誤的資料、忘記宣告變數、輸入到一半颱風來吹斷電線桿停電或者是上網到一半被隔壁屁孩射斷網路線這種諸如此類的狀況(之前真的有朋友跟我說他的網路線被屁孩射斷)，因此如果沒有做好一些錯誤機制的防範的話，那麼系統在上線時是很容易降低客戶對於該系統的信任度，所以錯誤的處理上是非常重要的。",[16,26,27,28,32,33,36,37,40],{},"那麼為了避免這種狀況我們通常就會使用例外處理的方式處理，如果已經有開始撰寫 ES7 語法的人，相信非常的熟悉 ",[29,30,31],"code",{},"async","、",[29,34,35],{},"await"," 語法，想當然你也一定會使用 ",[29,38,39],{},"try...catch"," 語法，下面簡單寫一小段：",[42,43,48],"pre",{"className":44,"code":45,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","\nasync function getData () {\n  try{\n    const res = await axios.get('xxxx');\n  } catch (error) {\n    console.error(error);\n  }\n}\n","js","",[29,49,50,59,76,85,117,129,141,147],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,52,55],"span",{"class":53,"line":54},"line",1,[51,56,58],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":57},true,"\n",[51,60,62,65,68,72],{"class":53,"line":61},2,[51,63,31],{"class":64},"sWyjQ",[51,66,67],{"class":64}," function",[51,69,71],{"class":70},"sj_SG"," getData",[51,73,75],{"class":74},"sMAXC"," () {\n",[51,77,79,82],{"class":53,"line":78},3,[51,80,81],{"class":64},"  try",[51,83,84],{"class":74},"{\n",[51,86,88,91,95,98,101,104,107,110,114],{"class":53,"line":87},4,[51,89,90],{"class":64},"    const",[51,92,94],{"class":93},"sCcAr"," res",[51,96,97],{"class":64}," =",[51,99,100],{"class":64}," await",[51,102,103],{"class":74}," axios.",[51,105,106],{"class":70},"get",[51,108,109],{"class":74},"(",[51,111,113],{"class":112},"sTRMh","'xxxx'",[51,115,116],{"class":74},");\n",[51,118,120,123,126],{"class":53,"line":119},5,[51,121,122],{"class":74},"  } ",[51,124,125],{"class":64},"catch",[51,127,128],{"class":74}," (error) {\n",[51,130,132,135,138],{"class":53,"line":131},6,[51,133,134],{"class":74},"    console.",[51,136,137],{"class":70},"error",[51,139,140],{"class":74},"(error);\n",[51,142,144],{"class":53,"line":143},7,[51,145,146],{"class":74},"  }\n",[51,148,150],{"class":53,"line":149},8,[51,151,152],{"class":74},"}\n",[16,154,155,156,158,159,162],{},"上面的程式碼簡單來講，就是當 AJAX 因意外失敗或者網路中斷時，就會自動改跑 ",[29,157,125],{}," 區塊，但是這邊要注意如果你是用於前端畫面給使用者看的話，請不要使用 ",[29,160,161],{},"console.log"," 當作錯誤提示，因為普通的使用者根本不知道什麼是網頁開發者工具(devToole)，因此這邊只是一個範例程式碼而已。",[16,164,165],{},[166,167],"img",{"alt":168,"src":169},"不知道為什麼系統出錯的使用者","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E6%A2%97%E5%9C%96%E5%89%B5%E4%BD%9C-1631979362.png",[16,171,172],{},"而上方是一個簡單的例外錯誤處理，接下來我們將會進入 Python 環節了解 Python 的例外處理是如何撰寫的唷！",[12,174,175],{"id":175},"例外處理",[16,177,178],{},"一開始先我們刻意製造一個錯誤狀況：",[42,180,184],{"className":181,"code":182,"language":183,"meta":47,"style":47},"language-py shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","def sayHello():\n  print('Hello')\n\nprint(myName)\n\nsayHello()\n","py",[29,185,186,191,196,200,205,209],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,187,188],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,189,190],{},"def sayHello():\n",[51,192,193],{"class":53,"line":61},[51,194,195],{},"  print('Hello')\n",[51,197,198],{"class":53,"line":78},[51,199,58],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":57},[51,201,202],{"class":53,"line":87},[51,203,204],{},"print(myName)\n",[51,206,207],{"class":53,"line":119},[51,208,58],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":57},[51,210,211],{"class":53,"line":131},[51,212,213],{},"sayHello()\n",[16,215,216,217,220],{},"上面的程式碼看起來很正常對吧？但實際上執行是會出現「",[29,218,219],{},"NameError: name 'myName' is not defined","」的錯誤唷~",[16,222,223],{},[166,224],{"alt":225,"src":226},"嚇到吃手手","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F1631980095440.png",[16,228,229,230,234],{},"oh!如果你問我為什麼會出現這個錯的話，罰你回去「",[231,232,233],"strong",{},"從 JavaScript 角度學 Python(4) - 型別與變數","」章節重看，因為這章節我有解釋唷~",[16,236,237],{},"那麼如果你這邊有使用例外處理的話，就可以避免程式碼因為錯誤而導致中斷，而讓後面其他的程式碼可以正常運作：",[42,239,241],{"className":181,"code":240,"language":183,"meta":47,"style":47},"def sayHello():\n  print('Hello')\n\ntry:\n  print(myName)\nexcept:\n  print('你忘記宣告變數了。')\n\nsayHello()\n",[29,242,243,247,251,255,260,265,270,275,279],{"__ignoreMap":47},[51,244,245],{"class":53,"line":54},[51,246,190],{},[51,248,249],{"class":53,"line":61},[51,250,195],{},[51,252,253],{"class":53,"line":78},[51,254,58],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":57},[51,256,257],{"class":53,"line":87},[51,258,259],{},"try:\n",[51,261,262],{"class":53,"line":119},[51,263,264],{},"  print(myName)\n",[51,266,267],{"class":53,"line":131},[51,268,269],{},"except:\n",[51,271,272],{"class":53,"line":143},[51,273,274],{},"  print('你忘記宣告變數了。')\n",[51,276,277],{"class":53,"line":149},[51,278,58],{"emptyLinePlaceholder":57},[51,280,282],{"class":53,"line":281},9,[51,283,213],{},[16,285,286],{},[166,287],{"alt":288,"src":289},"體會到例外處理好處的我妻善逸","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u00